OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOutbreaks of locally heavy rain
OL,6,Fgradually easing in the northwest.
OL,7,FHill and coastal fog with drizzle
OL,8,Faffecting western and southwestern
OL,9,Fareas. Elsewhere, turning brighter and
OL,10,Fwarmer. Becoming humid in the
OL,11,Fsoutheast later with showers, possibly
OL,12,Fthundery.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FOutbreaks of rain across
OL,15,FScotland and Northern Ireland. Low
OL,16,Fcloud and coastal fog across
OL,17,Fsouthwestern areas. Dry elsewhere with
OL,18,Fclear spells. Feeling muggy,
OL,19,Fespecially in the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
