OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FSpells of rain in the
OL,6,Fnorthwest edging southeast and fading
OL,7,Fwith showers following. Drier
OL,8,Felsewhere with sunny spells. Very warm
OL,9,For hot in the southeast and feeling
OL,10,Fmuggy.
